# Optimizing IT Support Team Performance Using Analytics

## 📌 Project Overview
This project focuses on analyzing IT support ticket data to identify patterns, improve operational efficiency, and optimize support team performance. The goal is to derive meaningful insights from ticket data such as resolution time, customer satisfaction, and issue distribution.

---

## ❗ Problem Statement
IT support teams handle a large number of tickets daily, but lack of proper analysis can lead to delays, inefficiencies, and low customer satisfaction. This project aims to analyze support data and identify key areas of improvement.

---

## 📊 Dataset Description
The dataset contains synthetic IT support ticket data simulating real-world scenarios. It includes:

- ticket_id  
- created_at  
- customer_id  
- customer_segment  
- channel  
- product_area  
- issue_type  
- priority  
- status  
- resolution_time_hours  
- customer_sentiment  
- csat_score  
- platform  
- region  

---

## 🎯 KPIs (Key Performance Indicators)
- Total Tickets  
- Average Resolution Time  
- Average CSAT Score  
- High Priority Ticket Count  
- Ticket Distribution by Channel  
- Ticket Distribution by Region  

